@N0122:          if fuel > 0.0 :
@N0124:              fuel -= burn
@N0126:  this should probably be 15
@N0132:  and do this again for yspeed
@N0143:          yspeed -= grav
@N0146:          ypos += yspeed
@N0154:  draw the rocket's position as a point
